# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Report / fixture build outputs (generated, never committed)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Seeders build fixtures deterministically; generated report outputs and any
# locally-built bundles stay out of version control. The committed, immutable
# fixture inputs under engine/fixtures/ are tracked explicitly by the seeders.
out/
output/
*.report.html
*.report.pdf
/engine/fixtures/**/_generated/
*.bundle.zip

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Editors / tooling
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/settings.json

